        <abstract>
            <para>All records of fungi, myxomycetes, algae and bryophytes available to HBRG including all those previously held on the database at IMAG. AAssembly and mobilisation of this dataset has been funded by grants from Scottish Natural Heritage (now NatureScot) since 2004, and in some years by members of the Highland Biodiversity Partnership.</para>
